ner of McCormick Place Parking Lot A. Rate is $23 for up to 16 hours. The Chicago Auto Show is a 10-minute walk from Motor Row Brewing.  RSVP by Friday, February 9 and find more details here .  For more information, please contact Maurice Willis, Associate Director of Engagement & Participation, at mwilli60@uic.edu or (312) 996-9422.      Modified on August 11, 2019                  UIC Logo         College of  Engineering            Contact   College of Engineering  851 S. Morgan St., MC 159, Chicago, IL 60607  Phone: (312) 996-3463  uic-engr@uic.edu        Social Media Accounts    Facebook    LinkedIn    Twitter    Instagram    YouTube             UIC.edu links   UIC.edu  Academic Calendar  Athletics  Campus Directory  Disability Resources  Emergency Information  Event Calendar  Job Openings  Library  Maps  UIC Safe Mobile App  UIC Today  UI Health  Veterans Affairs        Powered by Red 2.38.0  © 2020 The Board of Trustees of the University of Illinois |  Privacy Statement    Campuses   University of Illinois System  Urbana-Champaign  Springfield      Cookie Settings                   